title: Schrader-Lininger Education Town Hall in Lake Oswego (Clackamas County Democratic Party (Oregon))
text: ( Source : Clackamas County Democratic Party ( Oregon )) Clackamas County Commissioner Martha Schrader and state Rep. Ann Lininger will jointly hold a town hall meeting focused on education on Thursday, Oct. 8, at the Lake Oswego City Hall .
